\c 20
\s Zofari anoti mufaro wevatadzi ndewenguva diki
\p
\v 1 Zvino Zofari muNaama wakapindura ndokuti:
\p
\v 2 Naizvozvo ndangariro dzangu dzinondipindurisa, uye nekuda kwekukurumidza kwangu kuri mandiri.
\v 3 Ndakanzwa murango wechinyadzo changu, nemweya wekunzwisisa kwangu wakandipindurisa.
\v 4 Unoziva izvi here, kubva kare, kubva zvaiswa munhu panyika,
\v 5 kuti mupururu wevakaipa mupfupi, uye mufaro wemunyepedzeri ndewechinguvana?
\v 6 Kunyange ukuru hwake hukakwirira kusvika kumatenga, uye musoro ukananavira kumagore.
\v 7 Achaparara nekusingaperi sendove yake; vakamuona vagoti: Aripi?
\v 8 Achabhururuka akaenda sechiroto, uye haangawanikwi, hongu, achadzinganiswa sechiratidzwa cheusiku.
\v 9 Ziso raimuona haringapamhi; nenzvimbo yake haingazomuonizve.
\v 10 Vana vake vachatsvaka kufadza varombo, nemaoko avo achadzosera fuma yake.
\v 11 Mapfupa ake zere \add simba re\add*ujaya hwake, asi acharara paguruva pamwe naye.
\v 12 Kana uipi huchitapira mumuromo wake, achihuviga pasi perurimi rwake,
\v 13 asingahuregedzi, uye asingahusii, asi achihuchengeta mukati memuromo wake.
\v 14 Zvekudya zvake zviri muura hwake, zvichava uturu hwenyoka mukati make.
\v 15 Wakamedza fuma, asi achairutsa, Mwari achaibudisa mudumbu rake.
\v 16 Achasveta uturu hwenyoka; rurimi rwemvumbi huchamuuraya.
\v 17 Haangatarisi nzizi, nehova dzizere nouchi namafuta.
\v 18 Zvaakabatira achazvidzosazve, haangazvimedzi; haangavi nomufaro wakaenzana nefuma yake yaakawana.
\v 19 Nokuti akamanikidza nokurasira varombo; akatora imba nesimba, asi haangaivaki.
\v 20 Zvaakange asingazivi kudzikama mukati make, haangachengeti chinhu chimwe chaakange achifarira.
\v 21 Hakune chinhu chakasara chaasina kuparadza; saka kuguma kwake, hakungarambi kuripo.
\v 22 Pakati pezvakawanda zvefuma yake achamanikidzwa; ruoko rwomumwe neumwe ari panjodzi rucharwa naye.
\v 23 Kana achida kugutsa dumbu rake, Mwari achatuma kutsamwa kwake kukuru pamusoro pake, achakunisa pamusoro pake, zvive zvokudya zvake.
\v 24 Achatiza nhumbi yokurwa yamatare, uta hwendarira huchamuboora.
\v 25 Unoivhomora, ikabuda pamuviri wake; muromo wayo unobwinya, unobuda panduru yake; anotya kwazvo.
\v 26 Rima rese rakachengeterwa fuma yake, moto usina kupfutidzwa nomunhu uchamuparadza; uchapedza zvakasara patende rake.
\v 27 Kudenga-denga kucharatidza zvakaipa zvake, nyika ichamumukira.
\v 28 Zvakaunganidzwa mumba make zvichibva, nhumbi dzake dzichayerera pazuva rokutsamwa kwake.
\v 29 Ndiwo mugove womunhu akaipa waanopiwa naMwari, nenhaka yaakatemerwa naMwari.
